  <name>Linux Dev Home</name>
  <summary>Developer dashboard for Linux (Docker, metrics, Git, terminal)</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Linux Dev Home is an open-source desktop dashboard inspired by Microsoft Dev Home and VS Code–style visuals. It surfaces Docker containers, host metrics, bundled compose profiles, Git workflows, and an embedded terminal — all in a native Tauri application.</p>
    <p>Distribution is Flatpak-first for cross-distro compatibility. Docker socket, SSH, PTY, and /proc all work out of the box with full host permissions — no sandbox overrides required.</p>
  </description>
